Sayang talaga ang
kayamanan ng pamilya Gu.

00:26:19.112 --> 00:26:19.911
Marahil,

00:26:19.991 --> 00:26:21.431
lahat sila ay kukumpiskahin.

00:26:22.592 --> 00:26:23.512
Makinig.

