Ito...

00:36:26.071 --> 00:36:26.752
Ito...

00:36:27.792 --> 00:36:28.752
Saan ginawa

00:36:30.031 --> 00:36:31.391
saan nanggaling ang gansang ligaw na ito?

00:36:32.391 --> 00:36:34.632
Hindi ko ito kailanman pininturahan.

